		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><a name="8501"></a><span class="name"><span class="usercolor">Cennyan</span></span><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_offline.gif" border="0" align="absbottom" alt="Offline" title="Offline" /><div class="gensmall"><img src="images/ranks/rank_1.gif" alt="Enchanter" title="Enchanter" border="0" /><br />Enchanter</div><div align="left" class="gensmall">Joined:&nbsp;07 Oct 2003</div><div align="left" class="gensmall">Total posts:&nbsp;44</div><div align="left" class="gensmall">Location:&nbsp;The Nameless - Cincinnati, OH</div><div align="left" class="gensmall">Gender:&nbsp;Male</div></td>
                <td class="row1" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                        <tr>
                                <td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td><a href="viewtopic.php?p=8501#8501"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Tue Oct 28, 2003 10:57 am<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Soloing your VT Key</span></td>
                                <td align="right" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=8501"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>    </td></tr></table></td>
