                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">FG Shard - Get summoned weapons from mag/haste mask/belt thing.
<br />
Load bliss and mez, tash Guard Jontroy.
<br />
Charm Guard Jontroy.
<br />
Give him weapons and haste him and give him NDT.
<br />
Self invs.
<br />
Mez breaks run him slowly kinda of to the Shik'nar area.
<br />
Best way to charm him when u get there is to charm him in the valleys near the mouth of the cave to the Shik'nar.
<br />
Proceed to rip through all mobs.
<br />
This pet has low regen, so if he wont live, just gate. and come back in 1 hr if his health reaches 4%ish.
<br />

<br />
BTW, killing the shimmering spirit placeholders with gravity flux is a lot cooler. permanent illusion and scaled wolf helps too.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
