once there you can actually hug the arched wall to any of the spawns for hand in and gate out easy the only problem is the one remains (if yoru standing the center of teh arch against the wall there it's the most forward rigth spawn) killing this one will aggro ONE of the cloaked mobs, no more and not the armed duds above, snare/root him there and kill him without moving from the wall your fine, also having pets out don't seem to matter much maybbe unless you sit (unconfirmed) you can pacify this mob easily enough so you can kill the remains, it's the one looking from the same position is most forward right side of the ring of cloaked dudes. standing there with even 4 people never had anything but that one spawn aggro and got all four frames over a few hours. the hard part was getting into the room in the first place.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=319303" target="_blank" class="postlink">Olmec</a> <span style="font-style: italic">Let Them Come</span>
