                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Minor notes:
<br />
1&gt; In Ssra, You can't cast GoD on your pet.  =)
<br />
2&gt; Swarm-kiting works in ME.  Can get a shard/hour once you get good at it.  (I farmed for guildies).  Ask a bard how to swarm kite.
<br />
3&gt; Behind the "Royal Guards" (southmost blue dots) on the map are a good dozen light blue cleric mobs.  Don't fight near them, the'll CHeal your opponent.
<br />
4&gt; I find it is useful to zone if you get worms.  If you get 2 robes and no other aggro, just PBAOE Defence, mez, pacify and mem blur them.
<br />
5&gt; The Burrower in Acrylia is a very gimp NPC, easily single groupable, but not that much pet fodder.
<br />
6&gt; IVU works 100% (or at least 95%) in ssra mines.
<br />
7&gt; Use corners to fight in acrylia, silly.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
